w Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">AB mevzuatına uyum\r\nçalışmaları kapsamında, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">her iki Komisyon\r\nTüzüğünün de yürürlük tarihleri itibarıyla Türkiye'de uygulanabilmesini\r\nsağlamak amacıyla gerekli mevzuat çalışmaları yürütülmektedir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"color:#0F0F0F\">Yayımlanan AB Düzenlemeleri<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#0F0F0F\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-languag